        <h1>A Confession</h1>
        <p>Hi, Alaiza. I hope this message doesn’t come off as strange. I know lately naka notice ka siguro nga sige kog papansin sa imoha, whether sa social media or in person. I just want to be honest about it.</p>
        
        <p>Actually, it’s because I find you genuinely kind, warm, and very approachable. Ganahan kaayo ko sa vibes nimo, kanang calm ra pero comforting. What really struck me was katong time nga wala koy goggles, even though ginasunog na kaayo sa adlaw ug daghan kog issue ato nga time. Despite that, wajud ka nagduha duha nga pahiramon ko. Gamay nga butang para sa uban, pero dako kaayo siya para nako.</p>
        
        <p>Even sa uban moments nga kabalo ko nga naa kay gina-atubang nga issues ug kapoy ka, you still chose to be kind. Kana nga gesture, nakita jud nako ug na appreciate kaayo. Mao siguro ni nga mas nainspire ko nga maila pa ka ug tarong.</p>
        
        <p>I want you to know nga tanan nga ginabuhat nako nimo, ang pag-message, pag-check, ug pag-care is genuine. no lies, dili pa impress lang. It’s really coming from a place of sincerity and respect. I’m not perfect, but what I show you is real.</p>
        
        <p>So I’ll be direct, Lai. I really like you, and gusto nako ilihok ning na feel nako in a respectful way. But at the same time, I want to be very clear about this,  If ever wala kay gina-entertain karon or wala kay someone nga special sa imoha, I would really like to get to know you better. Dili ko magdali ug dili tika i pressure. Gusto lang nako nga klaro and tarung akong tuyo.</p>
        
        <p>If it’s okay with you, would you let me court you, slowly, sincerely, and with full respect for your boundaries?</p>
        
